meta.name: Laura Coates Live
meta.description: In Laura Coates Live, Laura goes inside the story with a relentless pursuit of the facts. She is CNN's chief legal analyst, playing a central role in the network's extensive legal programming.

videos.title: Episode 149
videos.overview: Analysis of CNN's exclusive interview with Vice President Kamala Harris and Governor Tim Walz: CNN aired The First Interview: Harris & Walz: A CNN Exclusive tonight at 21:00 with the 2024 Democratic Party's President and Vice President candidates. Harris and Walz sat down exclusively with Dana Bash from the battleground state of Georgia for their first joint interview.

videos.title: Episode 203
videos.overview: Tonight on Laura Coates Live, Laura was joined by Bluesky CEO Jay Graber for her first TV interview to discuss Bluesky's rapid growth, the community Bluesky seeks to create and foster, how Bluesky navigates content moderation, and more.

videos.title: Manhunt: The Search for the CEO Killer
videos.overview: The manhunt for the CEO killer is at 40 hours and counting in New York City. New clues are quickly pouring in and shaping a new picture of the gunman who murdered UnitedHealthcare CEO Brian Thompson. CNN reporters, profilers, and law enforcement experts explore and analyze this manhunt.

videos.title: Captured: Arrest in CEO Killer Manhunt
videos.overview: Police arrested the suspected New York CEO killer Luigi Mangione today at a McDonald's in Altoona, Pennsylvania. What led to his capture and what police found tying him to the crime are discussed and analyzed by CNN reporters, profilers, and law enforcement experts.

videos.title: Captured: Arrest in CEO Killer Manhunt
videos.overview: Luigi Mangione, the suspect in the killing of UnitedHealthcare CEO Brian Thompson, is fighting his extradition to New York, where he faces a murder charge. He was denied bail today during a court appearance in Pennsylvania. Law enforcement experts discuss more evidence that the police recovered with Mangione, like a 3D-printed black 9mm ghost gun with a black silencer.

videos.title: Captured: Arrest in CEO Killer Manhunt
videos.overview: New York Police Department state shell casings and fingerprints tie suspect Luigi Mangione to the murder scene of UnitedHealthcare CEO Brian Thompson. Law enforcement and legal experts review today's announcement, Mangione's increased isolation from family, and his mental state.
